Cutar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin Tarayyar Turai/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, suna ƙaruwa sosai tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Haɗakarwar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) ta nuna kamanceceniya tsakanin EU/EEA da United Kingdom, yana tabbatar da cewa ko da yake matakan sun bambanta daga ƙasa zuwa ƙasa, cutar ta COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Dangane da kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali dole ne su haɓaka shirye-shiryen su don karɓar yawan masu fama da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa da lafiya, musamman ma, kulawa mai ƙarfi.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an gano jerin cututtukan cutar sankarar bargo na kwayar cutar a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin China ta ba da shawarar sabon coronavirus a matsayin mai haifar da cutar, wanda yanzu ake kira da mummunan cutar numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An sanya sunan cutar ta coronavirus (COVID-19) saboda cutar ta SARS-CoV-2 ce ta haifar da cutar.
Shaida ta nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna da cututtukan cututtukan numfashi, tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma mafi yawansu sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin ɗari, COVID-19 yana da mummunan yanayi wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari ke da mummunan yanayi wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai zurfi.
Kashi 4 na mutanen da suka mutu a asibiti saboda COVID-19.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin haɗakar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin EU / EEA da United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma gwada adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK tare da waɗanda ke cikin Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Al'amuran COVID-19 a ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya sami ƙarin yaduwar ƙasa, kuma sauran ɓangarorin duniya na COVID-19 na yanzu suna bin yanayin a cikin wannan ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar Maris 5, 2020, na EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al, ya ba da rahoton farkon yanayin COVID-19 a Turai, kamar yadda WHO ta bayyana.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta sanar da tabbataccen lamari na farko guda uku da suka dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na China, a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
Ya zuwa ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami rahoton COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, tare da 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun jimillar adadin COVID-19 da kuma abubuwan da suka faru
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana yin rikodin COVID-19 na kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda ake sabunta bayanai a kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe ta amfani da tushen hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki, da WHO.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan don kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kuma kwatanta su da shari'o'in a Italiya.
A matsayin samfurin yaduwar COVID-19 masu aiki, mun ƙidaya adadin kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 masu haɗuwa, muna la'akari da yaduwar COVID-19 ta halitta a cikin kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin da aka ba da sanarwar a kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe, kuma mun gwada su da waɗanda ke Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin duka na 14 days na COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK ya yi kama da lardin Hubei (China) (Hoto 1).
A cikin EU/EEA da UK gaba ɗaya, haɗakar al'amuran COVID-19 sun fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu, sannan suka fara ƙaruwa sosai har zuwa 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (kayan aiki).
Wannan ya ƙunshi yawan adadin da aka ba da rahoton a Italiya, amma ya nuna cewa akwai karuwar adadin COVID-19 a duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya (abubuwan da ke ciki).
Shafi na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK, idan aka kwatanta da waɗanda ke Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa an riga an sami adadin masu cutar a cikin sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA 15 da Burtaniya, makonni 3 kafin ko ƙasa da 8 na safiyar ranar 15 ga Maris, kamar yadda aka samu a Italiya.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa COVID-19 yana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Halin da aka lura a cikin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa cutar ta ci gaba da ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bugu da ƙari, yayin da ƙasashe daban-daban ke cikin matakai daban-daban, rata tsakanin halayen lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da ma'anar yiwuwar yanayi daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe da kuma ƙa'idodin zaɓin marasa lafiya daban-daban waɗanda dole ne a bincika don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kamawa.
A farkon Maris 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun bayyana yanayin da ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci ga kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun nuna cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da hankali a cikin waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 a asibitoci da / ko cibiyoyin kulawa na ICU a halin yanzu suna samuwa ne kawai a cikin kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i a matakin EU/EEA (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Amma suna buƙatar tattara bayanan sa ido na yanzu a cikin tsari mai ma'ana wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin waɗanda aka ba da rahoton da kuma adadin mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin adadin gadajen asibiti na ICU da na matsakaici a Turai, wanda ya kai 29.2 a Jamus da 4.2 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa sauran ƙasashe suna da ƙasa ko fiye da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (kwana 12.5 na asibiti da matsakaitan asibiti a kowace mutane 100,000 a cikin 2010-11).
Yawan COVID-19 da aka yi asibiti a kowace EU/EEA da UK, yanayin samfurin da ke da alaƙa da wadatar kiwon lafiya yana da alaƙa da haɗarin wucewa > 90% na ƙarfin asibiti, wanda aka bayar a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC Rapid Risk Assessment na COVID-19.
Tun da yake har yanzu an iyakance shari'o'in zuwa wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin ICU suna ba da magani ga wasu ƙididdigar yanki, ya kamata a samar da bayanan shari'o'i da bayanan ICU, a cikin ma'anar cibiyoyin yanki, a cikin matakin Figure 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe suna nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa suna buƙatar shirya kansu don ci gaba da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa da lafiya da kuma musamman kulawa da gaggawa, kamar yadda yanayin ya faru a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
A kwanan nan, ECDC ta yi saurin kimanta hadarin da ke nuna cewa, maimakon jinkirta hana yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, ana buƙatar hanzari, aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar magance cutar, saboda idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri, saurin da ake tsammani na irin waɗannan shari'o'in ba zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci damar kimantawa, karɓa da daidaita martani ba.
An kuma lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a a cikin saurin kimanta haɗarin don kawar da tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan lokaci na dama yayin da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara ƙoƙarin su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba a kan kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan ya gaza, akwai yiwuwar cewa tsarin kiwon lafiya na sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA zai fuskanci ɗumbin marasa lafiya waɗanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai mahimmanci a cikin kwanaki da makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) ta barke ne sakamakon cutar sankara mai saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi (SARS) Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 3,000 da kuma kamuwa da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran kasashen duniya, kuma ya zama bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mai cutar daga batutuwa kuma yana nuna alamun kama da juna ta hanyar irin wannan tsarin.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin ƙarfi da mutuwa fiye da SARS, amma yana da ƙarancin kamuwa da cuta, kuma yana faruwa a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
A cikin amsa ga karuwar wallafe-wallafen game da cutar da ke tasowa, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙari ya samar da cikakken lokaci da kuma cikakken bita game da batun bincike mai tasowa.
Mun yi magana game da abubuwan da suka shafi cututtukan cututtuka, cututtukan cututtuka, cututtukan cututtuka, ganewar asali, magani, farfadowa da rigakafin cututtuka.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan cewa wannan bita zai taimaka mana mu fahimci kuma mu kawar da wannan mummunar cuta.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya kasance abin tunawa da ba a taɓa gani ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka gaya musu su zauna a gida saboda barkewar sabuwar cuta mai yaduwa a duk lokacin hutu da makonni da yawa bayan haka.
Wannan kwayar cuta tana da alaƙa da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar numfashi mai tsanani (SARS) a 2003, don haka a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, WHO ta sanya sunan SARS-CoV-2 da kuma cutar da ke da alaƙa da shi a matsayin COV Disease 19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma nan da nan ta bazu zuwa kasar da kuma wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
Har zuwa 2 ga Maris, 2020, cutar ta haifar da tabbataccen shari'o'in COVID-19 80,000, tare da fitar da sama da marasa lafiya 40,000 da mutuwar marasa lafiya 3,000.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "magabcin jama'a ne lamba daya" kuma mai yiwuwa ya fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), sama da bincike 200 da aka buga akan COVID-19 a cikin watanni biyu, sun hada da ilimin kwayar cutar, cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin cututtukan cuta, ganewar asali da magani, wanda ya sanya jerin kwayoyin cutar a cikin marasa lafiya daban-daban tun lokacin da aka fara rahoton shari'ar farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙarin taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sabon da kuma ci gaba da ci gaba da batun.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da CoV, da kuma cutar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar cutar a shekarar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafin cuta da kuma ci gabanta, da kuma wasu batutuwa na gaggawa da suka rage.
CoVs an saba da su a matsayin masu cutarwa da ba su da haɗari ga mutane, suna haifar da kusan kashi 15% na cututtukan sanyi.
Amma a wannan karni, mun fuskanci cututtuka biyu masu haɗari na CoVs na mutum, SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, waɗanda suka fara fitowa a China a 2003 da Saudi Arabia a 2012, kuma nan da nan suka bazu zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da mummunan lalacewa da mutuwa.
Saboda haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine ɓarkewar CoV na uku a cikin tarihin ɗan adam na kwanan nan.
