SARS-CoV-2 an gano shi a matsayin sabon nau'in beta-CoV wanda aka gano 99.98% na asalin kwayoyin halittar a cikin jerin samfura 10 da aka ɗauka daga cibiyar asalin cutar, kasuwar abincin teku ta Huanan a Huanan.
SARS-CoV-2 ya fi kama da MERS-CoV a cikin kwayoyin halitta fiye da SARS-CoV.
Ta hanyar watsawar lantarki, an gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin ƙananan ƙananan ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta na ƙwayoyin cuta na mutum.
An gano ACE2 na ɗan adam a matsayin mai karɓar SARS-CoV-2 da SARS-CoV.
Koyaya, furotin S na SARS-CoV-2 yana ɗaure ACE2 na ɗan adam da rauni fiye da furotin S na SARS-CoV, wanda ke haifar da ƙananan kamuwa da cuta daga SARS-CoV-2 fiye da SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 na iya samar da sabon ƙaramin furotin, wanda aka tsara ta hanyar orf3b, kuma furotin da aka yi amfani da shi wanda aka tsara ta hanyar orf8.
Wataƙila orf3b na SARS-CoV-2 na iya taka rawa a cikin kwayar cutar mai yaduwa da kuma hana bayyanar IFNß; duk da haka, orf8 ba shi da wani sanannen yanki ko manufa.
A ranar 18 ga Fabrairu, 2020, Zhou, et al. sun nuna cewa tsarin cryo-EM na tsawon tsawon mutum ACE2 a ƙuduri 2.9 Å ya haɗu da amino acid mai ɗaukar hoto B0AT1.
Sun gano cewa tsarin da aka rufe da kuma wanda aka buɗe ya haɗu a matsayin dimer, kuma cakuda ACE2-B0AT1 na iya ɗaure sunadarai biyu na S, wanda ke ba da tabbacin ganowa da kamuwa da cutar CoV.
B0AT1 na iya zama wata manufa ta warkewa don gwajin magani don shawo kan cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Mai watsa shiri na asali da na tsakiya
An san cewa SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV sun samo asali ne daga fararen hula kuma sun shiga mutane daga kuliyoyi da raƙuma, bi da bi.
Idan aka kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran CoVs, an gano cewa bat-CoV-2 na gida ne ga SARS-CoV-2 saboda sabon kwayar cutar tana da daidaito na 96% tare da bat-CoVZX45 da bat-CoVZX21 na SARS.
Koyaya, ba a san ko waɗanne matsakaita ne suka taimaka wa kwayar cutar ta ƙetare shingen nau'in don cutar da mutane ba, kuma hanyar watsawa har yanzu tana bayyana.
Ji, et al., sun ba da shawarar cewa macizai su zama masu jigilar abubuwa daga fararen hula zuwa ga mutane, wanda ya kamata a sami sake haɗuwa tsakanin jinsi a lokacin S furotin.
A cikin wani bincike, masu bincike a Guangzhou, China sun ba da shawarar cewa dogon hanci, mai cin naman alade, wanda ake amfani da shi sosai a cikin maganin gargajiya a China, na iya zama mai watsa shiri na SARS-CoV-2, wanda aka gano daidaiton kwayoyin halitta 99% tsakanin CoV da SARS-CoV-2 da aka gano a cikin naman alade.
Amma, bambancin kashi ɗaya cikin ɗari tsakanin kwayoyin halittar mutum biyu har ila yau babban bambanci ne, saboda haka ana jiran tabbaci mai ƙarfi don yanke shawara (Figure 33).
Ba a san halayen jiki na SARS-CoV-2 sosai ba.
SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV na iya rayuwa har tsawon awanni 48 a cikin bushewa da kuma tsawon kwanaki 5 a zafin jiki na digiri 20 da zafi na kashi 40 zuwa 50%.
SARS-CoV-2 yana da irin wannan halayen.
An nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 ba zai iya jurewa ba bayan minti 30 a cikin hasken ultraviolet da kuma a zafin jiki na 56 ° C, yayin da ether, 75% ethanol, maganin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta mai chlorinated, paracetic acid, chloroform, da sauran magungunan ƙwayoyin cuta ba tare da chlorhexidine ba zasu iya kashe shi yadda ya kamata.
A cikin al'ada, dukkanin 'yan adam ba su da kariya ga SARS-CoV-2 kuma saboda haka suna da rauni ga wannan sabon kwayar cutar.
A halin yanzu, babu wani bincike mai zurfi game da amsawar rigakafi ga SARS-CoV-2.
Saboda haka, za mu iya komawa ga wasu nazarin CoVs, musamman SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV (Figure 4).
A yadda aka saba, lokacin da kwayar cutar ta kai hari ga mai masaukin, ana gano ta da farko ta hanyar masu karɓar tsarin ganewa (PRR), wanda ya haɗa da masu karɓar nau'in C-type lectin-like, mai karɓar mai kama da Toll (TLR), mai karɓar NOD-like (NLR), da RIG-I-like (RLR).
Ta hanyoyi daban-daban, kwayar cutar tana motsa bayyanar abubuwa masu kumburi, tsufa na kwayoyin dendritic, da kuma tsoma baki na nau'in I (INN), wanda ke iyakance yaduwar kwayar cutar da kuma hanzarta fashewar kwayar cutar ta kwayar cutar.
Amma, N-protein na SARS-CoV zai iya taimakawa cutar ta tsira daga amsawar rigakafi.
Ba da daɗewa ba, tsarin garkuwar jiki mai kyau zai shiga yaƙi da kwayar cutar.
T lymphocytes tare da CD4 + da CD8 + T kwayoyin suna taka muhimmiyar rawa a cikin kariya.
CD4+ T cells suna motsa B cells su samar da kwayar cutar ta musamman, kuma CD8+ T cells suna kashe kwayoyin cutar kai tsaye.
Kwayoyin T masu taimako suna samar da cytokines masu ba da taimako don taimakawa ƙwayoyin ceto.
Koyaya, COVID na iya hana T-cell aiki ta hanyar haɗa T-cell apoptosis.
Tsarin rigakafin jiki wanda ya ƙunshi abubuwa da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta kamar C3A da C5A, yana da muhimmanci wajen yaƙi da kamuwa da kwayar cutar.
Alal misali, ƙwayoyin cuta da aka samu daga marasa lafiya da suka warke sun kawar da cutar MERS-CoV.
A wani ɓangare kuma, ƙwayar cuta tana sa ƙwayoyin cuta su yi yawa a gida, kuma hakan yana iya sa a yi wa huhu da sauran gabobin jiki lahani mai tsanani, kuma a yanayi mai tsanani, zai iya sa a yi wa gabobin jiki lahani ko kuma mutuwa.
