Zazzabi shine babban bayyanar COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa tare da rashin bayyanar cututtuka ko wasu alamomi kamar tari mai bushe, rashin jin daɗi, ƙoshin tsoka, kumburi, ciwon kai, ɓacin hanci, rhinoria, ciwon kirji, zawo, amai da kuma amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya na iya samun dyspnea da/ ko hypoxemia bayan mako guda bayan kamuwa da cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, marasa lafiya suna samun ciwon numfashi mai tsanani, ciwon daji, ciwon ciwon shan magani, da kuma coagulopathy.
Ana bukatar a fara gano cutar a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da zazzabi da kuma/ko alamun numfashi da kuma zazzabi mai tsanani, ko da kuwa akwai wani rashin daidaito na hoto na huhu.
Wani binciken alƙaluma da aka yi a ƙarshen Disamba na 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98 cikin ɗari na alamun cutar zazzabi ne, kashi 76 cikin ɗari na tari ne, kashi 55 cikin ɗari na dyspnea ne, kuma kashi 3 cikin ɗari na zawo ne; kashi 8 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon iska.
