An gano wasu mutane da ke fama da cutar sankarar bargo a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba kuma an kula da su a asibitin lardin Hubei ta hanyar Dr. Zhang Jixian, wanda ya shaida wa Wuhan CDC a ranar 27 ga watan Disamba.
