An tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 daga China zuwa Koriya ta Kudu a ranar 20 ga Janairu, 2020.
Hukumar Lafiya ta kasar ta bayar da rahoton karuwar adadin wadanda aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 20 ga Fabrairu, wanda aka danganta ga taron sabon addini na Shincheonji Church of Jesus a Daegu.
An yi zargin cewa masu bautar Shincheonji da ke ziyartar Wuhan da ke Daegu ne suka haddasa barkewar cutar.
