Kuma ya haɗa da rage yawan mutuwar yara a cikin haihuwar gida.
Wani bincike na 2013 ya nuna cewa gyaran hanyoyin wanke hannu na iya haifar da ɗan ci gaba a cikin tsayin yara a ƙarƙashin shekaru biyar.
A ƙasashe masu tasowa, ana iya rage mutuwar yara da ke tattare da cututtukan numfashi da na farji ta hanyar sauya halaye masu sauƙi kamar wanke hannu da sabulu.
Wannan mataki mai sauki zai iya rage mutuwar mutane da kashi 50 cikin dari.
Matakan da ke inganta wanke hannu na iya rage yawan zawo da kusan kashi daya bisa uku, kuma yana iya zama daidai da samar da ruwa mai tsafta a cikin ƙananan masu samun kudin shiga.
48% na raguwar yawan zawo na iya danganta ga wanke hannu da sabulu. Wanke hannu da sabulu, wanda aka saba yi a gidaje, makarantu da al'ummomi a duniya, shine hanya mafi inganci da araha don hana zawo da cututtukan numfashi (ARI).
Ciwon huhu, wanda shine babban ARI, shine babban dalilin mutuwar yara 'yan kasa da shekaru biyar, wanda ke kashe kusan yara miliyan 18 a kowace shekara.
An kiyasta cewa guda miliyan 35 na yara suna mutuwa kowace shekara saboda zawo da ciwon huhu.
UNICEF ta ce, yin amfani da sabulu wajen wanke hannu kafin cin abinci da bayan wanka zai iya ceton rayuka fiye da duk wani allurar rigakafi ko kuma magani, yana rage mutuwar mutane da kashi biyu cikin dari da kuma cututtukan numfashi da kashi ɗaya cikin huɗu.
Ana haɗa wanke hannu tare da sauran ayyukan tsabtace jiki a matsayin ɓangare na ayyukan ruwa, tsabtace jiki da tsabta (wash).
Wanke hannu yana taimakawa wajen kare kai tsaye daga cutar Impetigo, wanda ke yaduwa ta hanyar saduwa ta jiki.
Wani mummunan sakamako na wanke hannu shine cewa yawan wanke hannu yana iya sanya fata ta bushe kuma ya cutar da fata.
Wani bincike da aka yi a Denmark a shekara ta 2012 ya nuna cewa yawan wanke hannu yana iya haifar da cututtukan fata kamar su itching da kuma zubar da hanci, wanda ake kira hand rash, ko kuma cututtukan fata, wanda ya fi yawa a tsakanin ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya.
Wanke hannu sau da yawa kuma ana ganin alama ce ta rashin tausayi na tunani (OCD).
Akwai lokuta biyar a rana inda ya kamata a wanke hannaye da sabulu don rage yaduwar cututtuka ta hanyar amfani da hannayena a baki: bayan zuwa gidan wanka (tashin jiki, fitsari), bayan wanke jariri (canja sutura), kafin a shayar da jariri, kafin a ci da kuma dafa abinci, ko kafin / bayan sarrafa nama, kifi ko kaji.
Sauran lokutan da ya kamata a bi da hanyoyin wanke hannu don hana yaduwar cutar sun hada da kafin da bayan kula da wani rauni ko wata raunuka; bayan tsotsewa, tari ko hanci; bayan taɓawa da kwandon dabba ko taɓawa dabba da sharar gida.
A ƙasashe da yawa, ba a wanke hannaye da sabulu sosai ba.
Wani bincike na 2014 ya nuna cewa Saudi Arabiya ce ke da kashi 95 cikin 100 na yawan masu wanke hannu, Amurka tana da kashi 77 cikin 100 na yawan masu wanke hannu, kuma China tana da kashi 23 cikin 100 na yawan masu wanke hannu. Wasu hanyoyin canza halayya yanzu suna nuna cewa wanke hannu da sabulu yana ƙaruwa a lokuta masu mahimmanci.
