Wasu nazarin da aka yi game da ƙaurawar ƙwayoyin cuta ta hanyar sabulu mai ƙwayoyin cuta sun kammala cewa ba za su iya ƙaura ba saboda ƙwayoyin cuta sun halaka ta hanyar kumfa.
