Saboda haka, ba a zaɓi maganin rigakafin tashin hankali na ƙwayoyin cuta don sabulu na kashe ƙwayoyin cuta ba, amma ba zai iya zama mai tasiri kamar yadda aka ambata ba.
Baya ga masu amfani da fata da masu kare fata, ingantaccen tsari kamar masu daidaita pH na iya ƙunsar acid (acetic acid ascorbic acid, lactic acid), antibacterial mai aiki benzoic acid, da sauran masu sanyaya fata (kayan lambu, bitamin, menthol, tsire-tsire). Wani bincike mai zurfi da Jami'ar Oregon School of Public Health ta gudanar ya nuna cewa sabulu suna da tasiri wajen hana cututtuka da kawar da ƙwayoyin cuta kamar sabulu na yau da kullun na masu amfani da trichlosan.
