Gudanar da haɗarin aiki na COVID-19
Kula da haɗarin aiki na COVID-19 shine aikace-aikacen aikin lafiya da kiwon lafiya don kula da haɗarin rigakafin cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kulawa da haɗari a wurin aiki ya dogara da yanayin aiki da yanayin aiki, wanda ya dogara da tushen kamuwa da cuta, tsananin cutar a cikin al'umma, da kuma abubuwan haɗarin kowane ma'aikaci wanda zai iya zama mai rauni ga COVID-19.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Lafiya da Lafiya ta Amurka (OSHA), ayyukan da ke da ƙananan haɗarin kamuwa da cuta suna da ƙarancin hulɗa da mutane da sauran abokan aiki, waɗanda aka ba da shawarar matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta, gami da wanke hannu, ƙarfafa ma'aikata su zauna a gida yayin rashin lafiya, ladabi na numfashi, da tsabtace wuri na yau da kullun da kuma kashe kwayoyin cuta.
Ayyuka masu matsakaicin haɗarin kamuwa da cuta sun haɗa da ayyukan da ke buƙatar haɗuwa ta kai tsaye ko kusa da waɗanda ba a san ko ba a yi zargin cewa suna da COVID-19 ba, amma waɗanda za su iya kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar jama'a ko tafiya ta duniya.
Wannan ya haɗa da ma'aikata da suke hulɗa da jama'a, kamar su makarantu, wuraren aiki masu yawan jama'a, da kuma wasu manyan wuraren sayar da kaya.
Baya ga matakan rigakafin kamuwa da cuta, kula da haɗari ga wannan rukunin ya haɗa da kula da iska ta amfani da matattarar iska mai ƙarfi, amfani da masu tsaron sneez, da kuma samun kayan kariya na mutum idan mutum ya fuskanci COVID-19.
OSHO tana ɗaukar ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da ma'aikatan jana'izar da suka haɗu da wanda aka sani ko wanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19 a matsayin haɗarin kamuwa da cuta, wanda ya haɗa da ma'aikacin da ke aiwatar da aikin samar da aerosol ko tattara ko sarrafa samfuran wanda aka sani ko wanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19, wanda ke ƙara haɗarin kamuwa da cutar.
Hanyoyin sarrafa haɗari waɗanda suka dace da waɗannan ma'aikata sun haɗa da sarrafa injiniya kamar ɗakunan iska masu matsin lamba da kayan kariya na mutum wanda ya dace da takamaiman aikin.
