Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafi na Amurka (CDC) sun ba da shawarar cewa ma'aikata waɗanda ke nuna alamun cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani su zauna a gida har tsawon awanni 24 ba tare da shan maganin rage zazzabi ko wasu magungunan da ke canza alamun ba, har sai suna da zazzabi, alamun zazzabi da sauran alamun, kuma akwai manufofin hutu na rashin lafiya masu sassauci, waɗanda ke ba ma'aikata damar zama a gida don kula da dangin su da ke rashin lafiya, kuma ma'aikata sun san waɗannan manufofin.
OSHA ta ce, ayyukan da ke da matsakaicin haɗarin kamuwa da cuta sun haɗa da ayyukan da ke buƙatar haɗuwa da mutane masu nisan ƙafa shida (1.8 m) waɗanda ba a san ko ba a yi zargin cewa suna da cutar COVID-19 ba, amma saboda yaduwar al'umma da ke gudana a kusa da yankin kasuwanci, ko kuma saboda mutumin ya yi tafiya ta duniya kwanan nan zuwa inda COVID-19 ya yadu, yana iya kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Wannan ya hada da sanya ma'aikata waɗanda suka sami hulɗa da jama'a, kamar makarantu, wuraren aiki masu yawan jama'a, da wasu manyan wuraren sayar da kaya, da sauransu. Ƙirƙirar ƙwarewar injiniya don sarrafawa da kuma mafi yawan haɗarin haɗari sun haɗa da shigar da filtata mai inganci, ƙara yawan hannuwan hannu, sanya masu toshe jiki kamar su sneeze guards na filastik, da kuma sanya windows a cikin windows don sabis na abokin ciniki. Gudanar da kulawa na lokaci don ƙungiyoyin haɗari da waɗanda ke da haɗari, samar da ma'aikata marasa lafiya waɗanda ke da sha'awar zama a gida, samar da kayan aiki na kama-da-wane maimakon haɗuwa ta zahiri, kafa shirye-shiryen horarwa daban-daban, samar da ingantaccen tsarin kula da lafiyar COVID-19, gami da rufe wuraren da ke da haɗari, kafa dandamali na horo da horo ga masu amfani da ke buƙatar yin aiki, samar da ingantaccen tsarin kula da lafiyar jama'a da kuma ingantaccen tsarin kula da COVID-19, samar da dandamali na sadarwa da horo ga masu amfani da ke buƙatar yin aiki, samar da hanyoyin sadarwa da hanyoyin sadarwa na yau da kullun, samar da hanyoyin sadarwa na yau da kullun, samar da hanyoyin sadarwa na yau da kullun da ke taimakawa wajen magance COVID-19.
Ma'aikata da ke cikin wannan rukunin masu haɗari ba sa bukatar yin amfani da na'urar numfashi.
Idan mutum ya kamu da cutar a cikin jirgin sama, matakan da suka dace don kare ma'aikata da sauran fasinjoji sun haɗa da ware mutumin daga sauran mutane na tsawon ƙafa 6, sanya memba na ma'aikata don kula da mutumin da ke fama da cutar, da kuma ba wa mutumin da ke fama da cutar abin rufe fuska, ko kuma gaya wa mai cutar ya rufe bakinsa da hanci da takarda yayin da yake tari ko tari.
Lokacin kula da matafiyi mai rashin lafiya ko taɓa ruwan jikinsa ko ɓangarorin da ke iya kamuwa da cutar, dole ne a saka safofin hannu na likita, kuma idan matafiyi mai rashin lafiya yana da zazzabi, yana yin tari ko yana da wahalar numfashi, dole ne ma'aikatan jirgin su sanya ƙarin kayan kariya na sirri.
Gloves da sauran abubuwa masu zubarwa dole ne a zubar da su a cikin jaka mai haɗari sannan a tsabtace kuma a kashe wuraren da ke da cutar. Don jiragen ruwa masu yawon shakatawa da sauran jiragen ruwa na kasuwanci, gami da jiragen ruwa masu fasinjoji, matakan haɗari sun haɗa da jinkirta tafiya yayin rashin lafiya da kuma keɓe kai idan akwai zazzabi ko wasu alamun bayyanar cututtuka a cikin jirgin.
A matsayin manufa, ana buƙatar bin diddigin likita a cikin ɗakin keɓewa. CDC ta ba da shawarar rufewa na ɗan lokaci don tsabta da kuma tsabtace jiki, ko da kuwa ana iya yada cutar a cikin al'umma ko a'a, a makarantu da wuraren kula da yara.
Inda yaduwar al'umma ta kasance mai matsakaici, ana iya amfani da manufofin nisantar jama'a, kamar dakatar da tafiye -tafiye na filin, taron jama'a da sauran manyan tarurruka, gami da koyar da motsa jiki ko azuzuwan addu'a ko cin abinci a gidajen cin abinci, ƙara tazarar tebur, sauya lokutan isowa da fita, iyakance baƙi marasa mahimmanci, da kuma kafa wuraren shakatawa daban don yara masu alamun cutar mura.
Idan akwai kamuwa da cuta a cikin al'umma, tare da dabarun nisantar zamantakewa, ana iya yin la'akari da rufe makarantu na tsawon kwanaki. CDC ta yi la'akari da cewa ma'aikatan tilasta bin doka waɗanda ke yin ayyukan yau da kullun suna da ƙananan haɗarin lafiya.
Jami'an tilasta bin doka waɗanda ke buƙatar yin hulɗa tare da wasu waɗanda ke da cutar COVID-19 ko waɗanda ake tsammanin suna da cutar, ana ba da shawarar su bi ƙa'idodin kamar yadda ake yi wa masu fasahar likita na gaggawa, tare da kayan kariya na mutum.
Idan akwai kusanci a lokacin kulawa, ma'aikata su tsabtace su da kuma kashe su ta hanyar amfani da mai tsabtace gida ko shafawa kafin sake amfani da belin aikinsu da kayan aiki, kuma su bi ƙa'idodin aiki don sarrafawa da kuma zubar da PPE da aka yi amfani da su, ware tufafi, da wankewa.
OSHA ta yi la'akari da wasu ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da na jana'iza da ke da babban ko kuma babban haɗarin kamuwa da cuta.
Ayyukan da ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cuta sun haɗa da isar da kiwon lafiya, taimako, dakin gwaje-gwaje da ma'aikatan jigilar likitoci waɗanda suka haɗu da waɗanda aka sani ko waɗanda ake zargi da cutar COVID-19.
Akwai haɗarin kamuwa da cutar a kan waɗanda aka sani ko ake zargi da cutar COVID-19 idan ma'aikata suna gudanar da aikin samar da aerosol ko tattara ko sarrafa samfurori daga irin waɗannan marasa lafiya.
Tsarin samar da aerosol ya hada da intubation, hanyoyin shigar da cuff, bronchoscopes, wasu tsarin hakori, da kuma gwajin ko tarin samfurin kai tsaye.
Ayyukan jana'izar da ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cuta sun haɗa da ma'aikatan da ke aiki a kan shirya gawawwakin mutanen da aka sani ko kuma ake zargi da cutar COVID-19 a lokacin mutuwa; idan sun yi autopsy, suna da haɗarin kamuwa da cuta sosai.
A wasu wuraren kiwon lafiya da kuma gine-ginen gawa, ƙwararrun iska mai guba na iya zama mai kyau.
Za a sarrafa samfurori tare da matakan tsaro na 3.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ba da shawarar cewa idan ana zargin masu zuwa da cutar COVID-19, to a ware su a cikin ɗakunan jira. Kamar sauran PPE, OSHA ta ba da shawarar cewa a ba da izinin yin amfani da na'urar numfashi ga ma'aikatan da ke aiki a cikin ƙafa 6 na waɗanda aka sani ko ake zargi da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
A cikin Amurka, dole ne a yi amfani da masks masu numfashi na N95 da aka amince da NIOSH, ko mafi kyau, a cikin mahallin cikakke, tsarin kariya na numfashi na rubuce-rubuce, wanda ya haɗa da gwajin lafiya, horo, da kuma binciken likita.
Wasu nau'ikan masu kare numfashi na iya samar da kariya mafi kyau da kuma sa ma'aikata su fi jin daɗi. WHO ba ta ba da shawarar yin kariya ga jiki gaba ɗaya ba, saboda COVID-19 cuta ce ta numfashi, ba ta yaduwa ta sauran ɓoyayyen jiki.
WHO ta ba da shawarar cewa ma'aikatan bincike ne kawai za su yi amfani da abin rufe fuska.
WHO ta ba da shawarar cewa ma'aikatan da ke tattara, kula ko jigilar samfuran numfashi na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 waɗanda ke cikin magani ba tare da wani aikin samar da aerosol ba, su yi amfani da abin rufe fuska, tufafi da safar hannu, ko kuma abin rufe fuska.
Idan an aiwatar da aikin samar da aerosol, a maimakon abin rufe fuska, a yi amfani da N95 ko FFP2 masu kariya na numfashi.
Dangane da isasshen isar da PPE a duniya, WHO ta ba da shawarar yin amfani da shinge na zahiri kamar telemedicine, tsabtace windows, don samun damar shiga cikin ɗakunan da ke dauke da COVID-19 tare da masu ba da lafiya kai tsaye tare da PPE kawai don takamaiman aiki, rage buƙatar amfani da PPE a gare su, amfani da abin numfashi ɗaya ba tare da rarrabewa ba yayin kula da marasa lafiya da yawa tare da ganewar asali, kula da daidaitawa a cikin sarkar samar da PPE, da kuma samar da sabis ba tare da ƙarfafa masu amfani da abin rufe fuska ba.
