B'angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ((ACE2)) enzyme ne wanda ke haɗe da ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
Ta hanyar rage adadin angiotensin -II da haɓaka adadin Ang ((1-7) yana hana aikin ACE2 na enzymes masu canza angiotensin (ACE) kuma saboda haka yana da alamar magani don maganin cututtukan zuciya da jijiyoyin jini.
An kira kwayar halitta na enzyme hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 wani zinc-containing metallolenzime ne wanda yake a cikin endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Kwayar ACE2 tana da yankin N-terminal peptidase M2 da kuma yankin C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter.
ACE2 shine kwayar halitta mai ƙarancin ƙwayar cuta wanda ke aiki ta hanyar enzymes a cikin ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu da sauran ƙwayoyin.
Ƙarin yankin kwayar halitta na ACE2 an cire shi daga wata na biyu mai suna transmembrane da ake kira shades kuma sakamakon haka an saki furotin mai narkewa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe ya narke cikin fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin kusan dukkanin gabobin jiki: an haɗa shi da membrane na nau'in II na alveolar a cikin huhu, enterocytes a cikin ƙananan hanji, endothelial ƙwayoyin jijiyoyi da jijiyoyi, da kuma ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jini a yawancin gabobin jiki.
ACE2 mRNA tana cikin ƙwayar kwakwalwa, a cikin tsakiya, a cikin hypothalamus, da kuma cikin kwakwalwa.
Aikin farko na ACE2 shine ya zama mai hana ACE.
ACE yana ba da damar hawan angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II mai ƙuntata jini.
ACE2 a madadinsa yana fashe amino acid na carboxyl-terminal daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana hydrolyze shi zuwa angiotensin mai kwakwalwa (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
[des-Arg9]- ACE2 na iya karya wasu peptides da dama, ciki har da bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana daidaita jigilar membrane na mai ɗaukar amino acid mai tsaka tsaki SLC6A19 kuma yana cikin cututtukan zuciya.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shigar da kwayar halitta ga wasu ƙwayoyin cuta, ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (wanda ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (wanda ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, ƙulla yankin enzymatic na ACE2 akan farfajiyar ƙwayoyin cuta tare da furotin na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 Spike S1 yana haifar da endocytosis, kuma ana iya samun sauyawar cutar da enzyme a cikin endosomes da ke cikin ƙwayoyin.
Shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar mai masaukin baki mai suna Serine Protease TMPRSS2 don yin amfani da S protein, wanda aka hana a matsayin magani mai yiwuwa a cikin binciken da ake yi. Wannan ya haifar da wasu yanke shawara cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin ƙwayoyin zai taimaka wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta.
Koyaya, yawancin ƙungiyoyin kasuwanci da hukumomin sarrafawa sun ba da shawarar ci gaba da daidaitaccen mai hana ACE da maganin ARB.
Wani nazari da aka yi a kan tsarin da aka yi da kuma wani bincike da aka yi a kan yadda ake yin maganin da aka yi a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, ya gano cewa "yin amfani da maganin hana ciwon huhu yana da alaƙa da rage haɗarin kamuwa da ciwon huhu da kashi 34% idan aka kwatanta da na rigakafi.
Bugu da ƙari, waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu, musamman waɗanda ke fama da bugun jini da kuma rashin ƙarfi, sun rage haɗarin shan maganin ACE.
Ko da yake tasirin ACE inhibitor bai kai na gaba ɗaya ba, amma amfani da ACE ya kasance mai alaƙa da rage yawan mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da cutar huhu.
Ana ganin sake hada mutum ACE 2 (rhACE2) a matsayin sabon magani don mummunan rauni na huhu, kuma an nuna ingantaccen yanayin hawan jini da kuma yawan iskar oxygen a cikin jariran aladu da ke da cutar lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
A cikin mutane, rabin rayuwar rhACE2 na kimanin awa 10, kuma yana ɗaukar mintuna 30 kafin ya fara aiki, kuma tsawon lokacinsa awa 24.
Yawancin sakamakon ya nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama mai ba da bege ga waɗanda ke da rashin haƙuri ga cututtukan da ke da raunin raunin renin-angiotensin-sistemic inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) ko kuma rashin daidaituwa na rashin ƙarfi. An kimanta rhACE2 da aka shayar a gwaji na asibiti don maganin cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani.
b-COVID-19 Apps aikace-aikacen software ne a cikin wayar hannu, waɗanda aka tsara don taimakawa sadarwa a cikin martani ga annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20, wanda shine, hanyar gano mutumin da ya kasance tare da mutumin da ke da cutar ("saduwa").
An kuma samar da aikace-aikace da yawa tare da tallafin gwamnati a wasu larduna da yankuna.
An tsara tsarin da yawa don ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen gano alaƙa.
An nuna damuwa game da sirrin sirri, musamman a cikin tsarin da ke bin diddigin yanayin yanayin masu amfani da aikace-aikacen.
Zaɓuɓɓukan da ba a taɓa yin amfani da su ba sun haɗa da amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rajistar abubuwan da ke faruwa tare da sauran wayoyin salula na mai amfani.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar da cewa za su haɗa ayyukan don tallafawa irin waɗannan aikace-aikacen masu tushen Bluetooth kai tsaye a cikin tsarin aikin su na Android da iOS.
A cikin haɗin gwiwa tare da Alipay a China, gwamnatin China ta samar da wani app wanda zai ba da damar 'yan ƙasa su bincika ko sun kasance cikin hulɗa da mutanen da ke da COVID-19.
An yi amfani da shi a birane fiye da 200 a China, kuma a Singapore, ana amfani da shi a wani app mai suna Trace Together.
An samar da manhajar ta hanyar al'ummar IT na gida kuma an samar da ita a matsayin mai budewa kuma za a mika ta ga gwamnati. Arewacin Macedonia ta ƙaddamar da app na "Stop Corona" mai tushen BlueTooth don tuntuɓar mutanen da ke da cutar da kuma saurin amsawa ga jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An haɓaka APP ta Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya.
Har zuwa 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, App yana jiran amincewa daga Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, 2020, gwamnati ta ce ana ci gaba da ci gaba da aikace-aikacen kuma za a samar da shi a cikin 'yan makonni. An kuma shirya irin wannan aikace-aikacen a Ireland da Faransa ("Dakatar da COVID").
Australia da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikacen da suka dogara da Trace Together da Blue Tooth na Singapore. Rasha tana da niyyar gabatar da aikace-aikacen geofencing don tabbatar da cewa marasa lafiyar COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow ba za su bar gida ba.
Ross Anderson, Farfesa a fannin tsaro na injiniya a Jami'ar Cambridge, ya lissafa wasu matsaloli masu yuwuwa a tsarin da ke amfani da aikace-aikace, ciki har da kuskuren kuskure da kuma rashin yiwuwar tasiri idan amfani da aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga ƙananan yawan jama'a.
Da yake nuna damuwa game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen "coronavirus" masu ɓatarwa ko cutarwa, Apple ya sanya iyaka kan irin ƙungiyoyi da za su iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da suka shafi cutar coronavirus a cikin shagon aikace-aikacen su, yana iyakance su ga "gwamnati" ko kuma sauran ƙungiyoyi masu daraja.
Google da Amazon sun kafa irin wannan takunkumi.
Masu fafutukar tsare sirri sun nuna damuwa game da tasirin sa ido mai yawa ta amfani da aikace-aikacen cutar ta Corona, musamman idan za a lalata abubuwan da aka tsara don sa ido da aka tsara don magance cutar ta Corona.
Kungiyar Amnesty International da wasu kungiyoyi 100 sun yi kira ga gwamnati da ta sanya iyaka kan irin wannan sa ido.
